<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.180809>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21 – 26. Endonura saleri sp. nov.: 21, habitus and dorsal chaetotaxy; 22, tubercles and dorsal chaetotaxy of head; 23, ventral chaetotaxy of the head and labium; 24, chaetotaxy of labrum; 25, ventral chaetotaxy of abdomen; 26, macrosetae Di and De Abd. II." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/180809/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.180810>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27 – 30. Endonura saleri sp. nov.: 27, chaetotaxy of antennal segments III and IV; 28, claw and tibiotarsus III; 29, chaetotaxy of tubercles dorso-lateral, lateral and subocular of head; 30, chaetotaxy of Abd. V (De + Dl + L) and Abd. VI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/180810/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

